description: Explores a man's quest for immortality and the lengths he goes to defy aging.

description: In West Hollywood's Russian district, Margarita lives out the American Dream: competing on a reality show. Will she slay, serve, or survive?

His friends must make a choice: stay loyal to Adamo or opt for the safety of themselves and their loved ones. They discover that the past won't let them go easily--and that the price of freedom is higher than they ever expected.

Over 90 years, eight encounters mark Octavio and Adela's tumultuous relationship, mirroring pivotal moments in Spain's history.

description: The enigmatic hero, a speechless child and a ragtag motley crew journey through a zombie filled apocalyptic landscape to seek refuge in a medieval fun park whilst being pursued by a unstoppable deranged lunatic.

description: A young man hatches a murderous plot to inherit his family's wealth.

description: Two fans are on a quest to recover 80s wrestling memorabilia after a grieving daughter outbids them to satisfy her father's dying wish.

description: Feature film based on the novel by George Orwell.

description: A couple struggle to learn the truth about the origins of their unborn child-- a demonic entity that emerges from the body.

description: A young street singer and a homeless veteran remedy dark times through friendship and music.

description: The 4 rascals decide to take matters into their own hands and plot their own plan to "solve" a love triangle.

description: Is a romantic drama that intertwines themes of love, society, and the impact of social media

And not only that - Alwina also left Willow a little crooked house and, above all, her witchcraft. But does Willow really want to accept this inheritance and everything that goes with it? And on top of that, she has to find three girls who also have the gift of witchcraft and save the forest together with them. But where? And above all, how? Fortunately, Willow is not alone, because Rufus the fox will not leave her side.

description: A late-night suicide hotline operator receives a disturbing call from someone claiming to be him, knowing personal details only he would know.

description: A media crew mistakenly ends up in the wrong country while trying to profile a musician. As they collaborate with locals to create a viral trend, relationships form amid an unfolding health crisis.

description: A small town musician pushes to carve out a place for himself in the new wave of Mexican-American music after a clip of him performing one of his songs goes viral.

Title: 448. Pintu Ki Pappi
description: A man starts a lucrative business with his uncle when they realise he has a special power in this romantic comedy.

Title: 449. Aghathiyaa
description: A group of entrepreneurs discover the dark history of a mansion when they attempt to turn a profit by converting it into a haunted house.

description: With Internal affairs on his back, a corrupt cop working for a crime boss must take out the competition if he wants to live long enough to leave town.

Title: 452. A Figgly Christmas
description: When Santa Claus crashes in the land of the Woodgies, Figgly has to help Santa and save Christmas.

Title: 453. By Design
description: A twist on the body swap genre.

Title: 454. Experiment 77
description: A doctor running a Women's Behavioral Center struggles to keep her patients stable when one of her colleagues is found dead and her own mental well-being begins to deteriorate.

description: Natasha Flynn, a coke-fueled London estate agent, hides her crumbling life behind luxury. When loan sharks offer cash to hide a kidnapped agent, she's dragged into London's seedy underworld, leading to a bloody, chaotic showdown.

Title: 456. Like Father Like Son
description: Eli's father awaits execution for murder. As Eli experiences violent tendencies himself, he takes drastic steps to break the family's cycle of brutality.

Title: 457. Ramam Raghavam
description: In a tale of deceit and redemption, a son's greed leads him to betray his honest father, a government official in India, but as he plots his downfall, unexpected revelations force him to confront his own conscience.

description: A life affirming drama following different generations of an extended family searching for the same, near impossible thing: perfect fulfilment of life. Which proves to be a near impossible task.

description: A young Black man who is interning as a slave reenactor at a living history museum discovers that his white girlfriend's ancestors once owned his.

Unable to provide a logical explanation to those close to him, he cuts off contact with his past. From that moment on, he will have to survive without money, a home, and without speaking the language.

Title: 465. Wish You Were Here!
description: A man's life is told through 3 parallel time lines that alter his perception of science and religion to turn his whole world upside down.

Title: 490. Delusyon
description: A desperate wife whose husband is shot after a robbery attempt. Desperate to help him financially, she turns to Kap, a man who's always been interested in her, sparking an affair that shatters their relationships

Title: 491. Diablo
description: Kris Chaney, a recently released ex-convict embarks on a perilous mission. He kidnaps Elisa, daughter of Vicente, a powerful gangster, which puts them in danger from El Corvo, a psychopathic killer seeking revenge against Vicente's family.

Title: 492. June and John
description: Fascinated by an enigmatic woman who steals his attention, an ordinary man whose life is marked by monotony finds himself immersed in an intense romance that drags him into an unpredictable journey.

Title: 493. The Baby in the Basket
description: A baby in a basket is left on the steps of an isolated monastery on a Scottish island. The nuns take it in, planning to care for it until a storm passes. Soon though, strange and unexplained events begin to happen at the convent.

Title: 494. Descendent
description: A troubled LA school guard, haunted by family tragedy, experiences strange visions after a mysterious light appears in the sky. As his wife's due date approaches, he races to face his demons before his growing obsession consumes him.

Title: 495. Becoming Katharine Graham
description:
Becoming Katharine Graham tells the story of a painfully shy woman's accidental rise to power and how it changed history.

Born in 1917, Katharine Graham-known as "Kay"-was raised to adhere to the expectation that men would have careers, and women would raise the family. Kay, like most other women at the time, abided by these societal norms. But the course of her life would drastically change once her father, financier Eugene Meyer, bought a struggling newspaper at public auction in 1933.

This struggling newspaper was The Washington Post, and it was on the brink of collapse. The paper's performance incrementally improved under her father's leadership; Mr. Meyer poured his own money into the business to ensure its growth. Then, in 1946, Mr. Meyer handed control of the newspaper over to the next generation. A product of his own times, Mr. Meyer never considered giving the "Publisher" title to his daughter, even though she had quietly participated in the initial struggle to keep the paper afloat and had worked as a journalist both in San Francisco and at The Washington Post. Instead, he bequeathed the title and two-thirds ownership of the paper to her husband Phil Graham exclaiming that "no man should work for his wife." The performance of the paper grew exponentially under Phil's leadership, but his suicide in 1963 left Kay with a leaderless newspaper and four young children, forcing Kay to decide whether to take over the cherished family business herself or sell it.

Although a self-proclaimed "doormat wife," Kay made the difficult and unprecedented decision to keep the paper in the family and run it herself. She initially imagined she would serve as a figurehead-a somewhat silent placeholder-until her eldest son, Don, could take her place as Publisher. Yet, over the course of the following decades, Kay proved to be a vocal and incredibly important leader of The Washington Post. She worked hard to learn the newspaper business inside out, while simultaneously gaining confidence in her own abilities and earning respect within the male-dominated industry.

Over the course of her career, she rose to become one of the most powerful newspaper publishers of the 20th century. Kay had the courage to publish the "Pentagon Papers", stand behind the paper's historic Watergate reporting, and withstand the infamous 1975 pressmen's strike that threatened the very existence of the paper.

At its heart, Becoming Katharine Graham highlights pivotal events of the 1970s that occurred under Kay's leadership difficulties she endured as one of the first female leaders in corporate America. Featuring interviews with colleagues, friends, and family, and relying heavily on archival footage to bring Kay's own voice to the forefront, the film presents a nuanced portrait of Kay and pays homage to her inspiring role as a trailblazer for women in both journalism and corporate leadership. Her Pulitzer Prize winning story is sure to inspire a new generation.

Title: 496. The Networker
description: Aditya, who is completely broken after the closure of the MLM company. The same Raghav tells Aditya about Lallan Miyan who is a experienced networker in the market. Lallan takes Aditya and Raghav to Pradhan ji and Pradhan ji likes the plan and invests in them. While the company was doing well, it suddenly faces a huge downfall. The company has to lend(close). Then Pradhan ji gives one last chance to Aditya and Raghav and invests again for the new company. Aditya and Raghav then hire a motivational speaker Gyani Baba, to promote their company. So that no one in the market comes to know that this company belongs to Aditya and Raghav, they hire an MD Pradeep for it. After collecting good funds in the company, Aditya , Raghav and lallan lend(close) the company and leave for Dubai.

Title: 497. Not Just a Goof
description: "Not Just A Goof" is a documentary exploring the untold story of "A Goofy Movie." It follows a young creative team tackling their first Disney feature, its initial disappointment, and its surprising resurgence decades later.

Title: 498. Caper
description: When a sext to the wrong number sends a group of clueless men into a panic, they recklessly dive into an all-night journey through NYC to save their friend, revealing their own misguided and toxic views on women along the way.

Title: 499. Six the Musical Live!

Title: 500. Haunting of Mount Gede
description: Two true friends who love each other. But there is a secret that is covered up then creates a disaster, and haunts their climb on Mount Gede.

Title: 501. 14 Days: Girlfriend Intlo
description: Harsha gets trapped in his girlfriend Ahana's house with no way of escaping with out being seen by her parents

Title: 502. Bunker
description: Trapped in an underground fallout shelter, six people fight to stay alive as oxygen - and trust in each other - runs out.

Title: 506. DSLR

Title: 507. Let's Meet

Title: 508. Alien Wars: Judgement Day
description: After an alien catastrophe, a few remaining human souls try to hold on to their sanity and their reality as humanity slowly slips into darkness.

Title: 509. Forbidden Fairytale
description: It follows Danbi, who dreams of being a children's book writer but is in reality a rookie on the illegal pornography crackdown team.

Title: 510. Forest
description: A dense forest conceals a hidden treasure, drawing five villagers into a humorous and action-packed hunt. They must outsmart a notorious criminal and a ghost who is fiercely guarding the treasure. Will they find the treasure?

Title: 511. Tokyo Nights

description: When a gunman enters an Apple Store in the heart of Amsterdam, the police face a delicate challenge to resolve the standoff. Based on true events.

Title: 517. The Black Box
description: A group of friends gathers for a farewell party that turns into a very peculiar truth or dare game.

A chronicle of the Mexican oil expropriation in 1938 through the eyes of President Lázaro Cárdenas and journalist Alberto Miranda.

description: In a flood-threatened village, Marko's life is turned upside down when Slaven returns for his father's funeral and rekindles their forbidden romance. Marko must confront his family and make a difficult choice.

description: Two best friends rally the neighbors of their tenement building to help them hide a dead body and get through the night.

Title: 562. Night of the Dead Sorority Babes
description: Two villainous entities initiate gorgeous sorority babes, will any pledges survive? Party 'til you drop - dead. The college girls want to join the sorority Gamma Rho Kappa but discover it hides a dark secret.

Title: 563. 100 dni do matury
description: This film is an engaging story about first important choices, friendship, and change, featuring top Polish influencers. A smart and funny movie for teenagers, blending an important message with quality entertainment and daring action.

Title: 564. LifeHack
description: Four teenage slackers attempt a multi-million-dollar Bitcoin heist from their bedrooms, only to spiral into the darkest corners of the internet-and a danger beyond their computer screens.

Title: 565. Atlantis the Fallen Empire
description: Following the fall of the eastern temple led by the kingdom of Athens. Atlas (The King of Atlantis) and his men must venture off into Hades with the help of Khonsu (The exiled Pharaoh of Egypt) in seek of the crystals of Pandora in order to save their Empire.

Title: 566. The Secret Agent

Title: 567. Sauna

description: A woman spends the night fighting for her existence as she slips down a rabbit hole contained inside a gift from a late-night visitor

description: Erin and Charlie escape to the desert to navigate an unexpected and challenging new phase of their relationship.

description: A 12 years old boy causes a serious accident and the only witness is his father who has to decide between lying or letting his son go to juvie. He chooses to lie but what are the consequenses?

description: Celebrity stylist/fashion icon, Dwen Curry, secretly finances a lavish lifestyle by fraudulently acquiring millions using her criminal organization, while grappling with family, love, identity, and the dangers of leading a criminal life.

Title: 574. Nonnas

Title: 575. Girl in the Garage: The Laura Cowan Story

Amid broken truces and escalating tensions, the fearless Sardars must rise against overwhelming odds to protect their land. Will they prevail against this formidable foe?
